snippet.title: Miranda Lambert - The Weight Of These Wings - Album Review
snippet.description:
For my 669th review, I dig into the morally ambigious haze of Miranda Lambert's most ambitious project to date.

Best Songs: 'Getaway Driver', 'Pushin' Time', 'Tin Man', 'Use My Heart', 'Runnin' Just In Case', 'Well-Rested'
Worst Songs: 'Bad Boy'

7/10

To skip my preamble, go to 1:42

Text review of 'The Weight Of These Wings': http://www.spectrum-pulse.ca/2016/11/album-review-weight-of-these-wings-by.html

My first ever full-length novel, 'To Kill A Dragon'! http://morningrainpublishing.com/project/to-kill-a-dragon/

Special thanks to Jillboard100 for the outro video design - definitely check out the channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Jillboard100 

If you want to read the review in text, or check out any additional reviews I've done so far, go to http://www.spectrum-pulse.ca for more. Otherwise, be sure to like and subscribe for more!

Follow me on Twitter at https://twitter.com/SpectrumPulse

Thanks for watching!
